reviewText: DVD skips/scratchy sound, very difficult to watch. Definitely disappointed.

One of the BEST Wow Wow Wubbzy DVD combos I've purchased so far. My two youngest sons ages three and five love this collection!! All four DVDs are separate in the case. Its just a fun and awesome collection!
My kids love Wubbzy.  I found this four pack cheaper then some of the movies were individually.
